The canonical rules for this repo live in `.ai/`. Read them and follow them:

- @.ai/rules/00-overview.md
- @.ai/rules/10-tech-stack.md
- @.ai/rules/20-conventions.md
- @.ai/rules/30-workflow.md

Skills (task recipes) are in `.ai/skills/`; agent roles in `.ai/agents/`.

## Essentials

- Astro v5 (static) + React 19 islands + Tailwind v4; trilingual **en / zh-hk /
  ja** (English default). Voice: "Build first, then talk." (zero-upfront-cost,
  AI-driven prototype first).
- **kebab-case** filenames; component-folder convention
  (`<name>/{<name>.astro|tsx, index.ts, types.ts, constants.ts, hooks.ts,
  hooks.test.ts}`). Every `hooks.ts` needs a `hooks.test.ts` (Vitest).
- All copy in `src/i18n/ui.ts`, filled for all three locales. Style with
  `var(--color-*)`; never add color tokens inside `@theme`.
- Gate before committing: `pnpm lint && pnpm test && pnpm build`.

Design system: `DESIGN.md`.
